    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="设置国内的镜像"><a href="#设置国内的镜像" class="headerlink" title="设置国内的镜像"></a>设置国内的镜像</h1><p>windows下分两个命令执行<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">SET SASS_BINARY_SITE=https://npm.taobao.org/mirrors/node-sass/  <span class="comment"># --设置环境变量</span></div><div class="line">npm install node-sass   <span class="comment"># 安装</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
